Description: Vietnamese input method engine for GNOME (Wayland)
 ibus-bambusa is a Vietnamese input method engine for IBus, targeting GNOME on
 Wayland. It supports the Telex, VNI and VIQR typing methods, every common
 output charset, spelling validation, text macros and a libadwaita preferences
 GUI.
